          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two different irradiation procedures were used",
                " in order to determine the DN absolute yield.",
                "The first one consists  of  a  very  short irradiation",
                " (T-irr << T-1/2) and long decay time (t >> T1/2).  In",
                " this case  absolute  yield  is  proportional  to  the",
                " integral of the entire decay curve. The",
                "The second method is based on a very long  irradiation",
                " (Tirr >> T1/2) and followed by a long decay time.  In",
                " this case absolute yield is proportional to the  time",
                " dependent yield. at the beginning of the decay."
              ]
            }
          ],
